                <strong class="text-[#0d7377]">RFIDAK LF products:</strong>
                <a href="/product/rfid-keyfob" class="text-[#0d7377] font-medium hover:underline">RFID keyfob (EM / T5577)</a> \u2022
                <a href="/category/rfid-keyfob" class="text-[#0d7377] font-medium hover:underline">LF keyfob range</a> \u2022
